<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-19-0217 </DOCNO><TEXT>With visual, digital, radioscopic and scanner control, it is possibleto implant a capsule of 125 radioiodine in ENT tumours. The dosage iscalculated by a special method, with no risk of over or underdosing,or of internal radiation. 19 applications were effected between 1983and 1986, 15 of which were for recurrences. The treatment is palliative,effective and causes little disturbance.</TEXT></DOC>